7#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/AddExplicitTypeCasts.h"
8#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/AstHelpers.h"
9#include "compiler/translator/tree_util/IntermRebuild.h"
10
11using namespace sh;
12
13namespace
14{
15
16class Rewriter : public TIntermRebuild
17{
18 SymbolEnv &mSymbolEnv;
19 bool mNeedsExplicitBoolCasts = false;
20
21 public:
22 Rewriter(TCompiler &compiler, SymbolEnv &symbolEnv, bool needsExplicitBoolCasts)
23 : TIntermRebuild(compiler, false, true), mSymbolEnv(symbolEnv), mNeedsExplicitBoolCasts(needsExplicitBoolCasts)
24 {}
25
26 PostResult visitAggregatePost(TIntermAggregate &callNode) override
27 {
28 const size_t argCount = callNode.getChildCount();
29 const TType &retType = callNode.getType();
30
31 if (callNode.isConstructor())
32 {
33 if (IsScalarBasicType(retType))
34 {
35 if (argCount == 1)
36 {
37 TIntermTyped &arg = GetArg(callNode, 0);
38 const TType argType = arg.getType();
39 if (argType.isVector())
40 {
41 return CoerceSimple(retType, SubVector(arg, 0, 1), mNeedsExplicitBoolCasts);
42 }
43 }
44 }
45 else if (retType.isVector())
46 {
47 //1 element arrays need to be accounted for.
48 if (argCount == 1 && !retType.isArray())
49 {
50 TIntermTyped &arg = GetArg(callNode, 0);
51 const TType argType = arg.getType();
52 if (argType.isVector())
53 {
54 return CoerceSimple(retType, SubVector(arg, 0, retType.getNominalSize()), mNeedsExplicitBoolCasts);
55 }
56 }
57 for (size_t i = 0; i < argCount; ++i)
58 {
59 TIntermTyped &arg = GetArg(callNode, i);
60 SetArg(callNode, i, CoerceSimple(retType.getBasicType(), arg, mNeedsExplicitBoolCasts));
61 }
62 }
63 else if (retType.isMatrix())
64 {
65 if (argCount == 1)
66 {
67 TIntermTyped &arg = GetArg(callNode, 0);
68 const TType argType = arg.getType();
69 if (argType.isMatrix())
70 {
71 if (retType.getCols() != argType.getCols() ||
72 retType.getRows() != argType.getRows())
73 {
74 TemplateArg templateArgs[] = {retType.getCols(), retType.getRows()};
75 return mSymbolEnv.callFunctionOverload(
76 Name("cast"), retType, *new TIntermSequence{&arg}, 2, templateArgs);
77 }
78 }
79 }
80 }
81 }
82
83 return callNode;
84 }
85};
86
87} // anonymous namespace
88
89bool sh::AddExplicitTypeCasts(TCompiler &compiler, TIntermBlock &root, SymbolEnv &symbolEnv, bool needsExplicitBoolCasts)
90{
91 Rewriter rewriter(compiler, symbolEnv, needsExplicitBoolCasts);
92 if (!rewriter.rebuildRoot(root))
93 {
94 return false;
95 }
96 return true;
97}
